        public void addPredefinedGrammar(String name,
                                 String renameFileLocation)
        Adds a new predefined grammar (including its field maps) to the list of utilised grammars. If no predefined grammar is set so far, the necessary list and map is created.
        Parameters:
        name, - the name of the predefined grammar
        renameFileLocation, - the location of the file defining the map from fields of the predefined grammar to those of the analysed data structure.
